Arnold Daly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arnold_Daly 0 Arnold Daly (October 22, 1875 – January 13, 1927) was an American actor, playwright and producer. He was the father of actress and Algonquin Round Table personality Blyth Daly. Arnold_Daly ( October_22_,_1875 – January_13_,_1927 ) was an_American_actor , playwright_and_producer .
